short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyze the sheet by using the power of Gemini

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unearth insights from your Google Sheets with ease! This extension empowers you to:

Analyze data directly: Simply paste your Google Sheet URL and instantly access your sheet data.
Ask & receive answers: Craft questions about your sheet's content, and our powerful AI, Gemini, will provide informative responses.

Boost your workflow:

Save time spent manually retrieving and analyzing data.
Gain deeper understanding from your sheets through intuitive questioning.
Get started quickly:

Install the extension in just a few clicks.
No complex configurations required.
Powered by Gemini:

Leverage the capabilities of a large language model for insightful data analysis.
Note: This extension utilizes Google Sheets and interacts with Gemini, a large language model.
